items.title: The Heartbreaking Notes Pinned To Babies Left On The Steps Of A 19th Century Asylum
items.description: “My Dear Good Sister, please accept this little outcast son of mine trusting with God’s help that I will be able to sustain him in your institution. I would not part with my baby were it in any way possible to make a respectable living with him, but I cannot... his name is Joseph Cavalier.”
